<Title>Двумерное БПФ</Title>
<P>Для двумерного БПФ можно получить следующий аналог &quot;бабочки&quot;</P>
<P><Formula>V(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)=S<Sub>00</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)+W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>01</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)+W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>10</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)+W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub>+k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>11</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)</Formula> ;</P>
<P> <Formula Br="Y" Num="Y" ID="ETK8ADGC">V(k<Sub>1</Sub>+<Fraction><M>N</M><M>2</M></Fraction>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)=S<Sub>00</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)+W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>01</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)-W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>10</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)-W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub>+k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>11</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>) ;</Formula></P>
<P><Formula>V(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>+<Fraction><M>N</M><M>2</M></Fraction>)=S<Sub>00</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)-W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>01</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)+W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>10</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)-W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub>+k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>11</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>) ;</Formula></P>
<P><Formula>V(k<Sub>1</Sub>+<Fraction><M>N</M><M>2</M></Fraction>,k<Sub>2</Sub>+<Fraction><M>N</M><M>2</M></Fraction>)=S<Sub>00</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)-W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>01</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)-W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>10</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)+W<Free><M Y="1.0">k<Sub>1</Sub>+k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N</M></Free>S<Sub>11</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)</Formula></P>
<P>где </P>
<P><Formula>S<Sub>00</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)=<Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>=0</M></Matrix><Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>2</Sub>=0</M></Matrix>U(2m<Sub>1</Sub>,2m<Sub>2</Sub>)W<Free Dy="0.0"><M Y="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>k<Sub>1</Sub>+m<Sub>2</Sub>k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N<Sub>1</Sub></M></Free></Formula>;</P>
<P /><P><Formula Br="Y" Num="Y" ID="ETK90JF1">S<Sub>01</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)=<Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>=0</M></Matrix><Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>2</Sub>=0</M></Matrix>U(2m<Sub>1</Sub>,2m<Sub>2</Sub>+1)W<Free Dy="0.0"><M Y="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>k<Sub>1</Sub>+m<Sub>2</Sub>k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N<Sub>1</Sub></M></Free>;</Formula></P>
<P>S<Sub>10</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)=<Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>=0</M></Matrix><Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>2</Sub>=0</M></Matrix>U(2m<Sub>1</Sub>+1,2m<Sub>2</Sub>)W<Free Dy="0.0"><M Y="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>k<Sub>1</Sub>+m<Sub>2</Sub>k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N<Sub>1</Sub></M></Free>;</P>
<P>S<Sub>11</Sub>(k<Sub>1</Sub>,k<Sub>2</Sub>)=<Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>=0</M></Matrix><Matrix Col="1" Row="3" Alg="0"><M X="0.5" Y="1.2" Kh="1.0">N<Sub>1</Sub>-1</M><M X="0.5" Y="2.6" Kh="1.0">&#x2211;</M><M X="0.5" Y="4.0" Kh="1.0">m<Sub>2</Sub>=0</M></Matrix>U(2m<Sub>1</Sub>+1,2m<Sub>2</Sub>+1)W<Free Dy="0.0"><M Y="1.0">m<Sub>1</Sub>k<Sub>1</Sub>+m<Sub>2</Sub>k<Sub>2</Sub></M><M Y="2.5">N<Sub>1</Sub></M></Free></P>
